br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8790defb1f7bac97ca6e7a169d8626d61a0f6a3b","tid":1534431,"uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"直接講物管師，佢地會跪到咸"},{"pid":"fdec6d1f78f242ef67cb88ae7f2afd574cbab853","tid":1534431,"uid":187714,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"起完底 假膠波台狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完</span></span>"},{"pid":"a11fde6710d1d94489091dd0e6c4a86f10209c19","tid":1534431,"uid":22924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:42:13.000Z","msg":"比人話老豆做狗<br />\n要慘話比人話老母係雞係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e138fe97c123a475c9a31551fbb70f142935830","tid":1534431,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"ccabb1dec775b40d6ac97381738d834b9655d802","tid":1534431,"uid":248571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11fde6710d1d94489091dd0e6c4a86f10209c19","tid":1534431,"uid":22924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:42:13.000Z","msg":"比人話老豆做狗<br />\n要慘話比人話老母係雞係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:28.000Z","msg":"係囉屌梗係澄清"}]}